main event: Several objects were seen on radar, making abrupt turns and moving swiftly.
interesting points: The sighting was recorded under Project 10073, likely part of Project Blue Book., The objects' movements were described as abrupt and swift., Investigation team concluded that the sightings could be attributed to known causes like balloons or aircraft., There was no confirmation of the objects by other radar sites., The length of the observation was approximately 5 minutes.
